{"tid":1434331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家，香港人已經唔可以再輸","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:07:41.000Z","uid":254809,"like":84,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4c49326c3d7227f3b9981aa49f1639ea9f9d7c","tid":1434331,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:44:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有冇發覺近排大家好歡樂，每次上連登都大把嘢可以笑<br />\n<br />\n笑下把雷射槍，又笑下福建班人敗走，又笑下er...er...er...阿SIR</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實大家都轉移咗焦點呀</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正當大家都喺度笑梗雷射槍，同嗰個er...er...er...阿SIR</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇留意你哋忽略咗好多嘢？</span><br />\n有冇發覺，熱門嘅POST大部份都係 福建，記招，旺角精品？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇發覺熱門多咗好多膠POST？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">代表香港人已經慢慢放鬆梗</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府一直做咁多嘢就係想你哋轉移視線</span><br />\n你哋已經中咗計<br />\n再咁落去，<span style=\"color: red;\">5年前嘅歷史又會再重演</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人已經唔輸得㗎啦<br />\n適當咁放鬆係好事，<span style=\"color: red;\">但唔好畀自己沉醉喺歡樂當中</span><br />\n我哋已經慢慢步入5年前嘅尾段<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家有冇諗過輸咗會點</span><br />\n警權會無限大，到時冇得再叫佢哋警犬，係佢哋叫我哋做狗狗<br />\n監控系統會正式運作<br />\n義士會被逐一清算<br />\n真係至少十年冇得番身<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更壞嘅打算係一齊入集中營</span><br />\n唔好諗住冇可能，捉晒香港人去集中營有咩問題？大把中國人嚟香港取代你哋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v8zNPmBttAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv8zNPmBttAQ&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=36fceb2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v8zNPmBttAQ</a>"},{"pid":"34bc8683e10719e7bcb999826907c72215943ca9","tid":1434331,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:44:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba05e52e4194e878562f5c4121b866217b0165a6","tid":1434331,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"